  "detailed_description": "A memory training game that let you memorize the order of one shuffled deck of 52 playing cards in minutes. Memorize a deck of cards is a classic event of World Memory Championships. Turn a gamer to a Master of Memory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Customize card, include graph and words. You can use any image as poker face.<br></li><li> Shuffle deck.<br></li><li> View cards, and make a story with scene, character, spell and equipment.<br></li><li> Examine.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Suit Definition</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> ♥ Character<br></li><li> ♣ Scene<br></li><li> ♦ Spell<br></li><li> ♠ Equipment</li></ul>",
